Summary¶

Regime $S_1$ $S_2$ $S_3$
Normal $S_v$ $S_{Hmax}$ $S_{hmin}$
Strike-slip $S_{Hmax}$ $S_{v}$ $S_{hmin}$
Reverse $S_{Hmax}$ $S_{hmin}$ $S_{v}$
